Package com.soa.console.binding

Interface Summary
AccessPointContext The AccessPointContext is an access point context interface containing information regarding access point implementation including its WSDL port implementation.
AccessPointPortletRenderer The AccessPointPortletRenderer is a template interface for displaying binding specific access point content in a portlet that is used by the Governance Console.
AccessPointWizardRenderer The AccessPointWizardRenderer is a template interface for displaying binding specific physical and/or virtual access point content in a wizard that is used by the Governance Console.
BindingContext The BindingContext is wsdl binding context interface containing information regarding wsdl binding implementation.
BindingWizardRenderer The BindingRenderer is a template interface for displaying binding specific content in a wizard that is used by the Governance Console.
 

Class Summary
AccessPointContextLoader The AccessPointContextLoader is used to retrieve and set access point context from the servlet request context.
BindingContextLoader The BindingContextLoader is used to retrieve and set binding context from the servlet request context.
